Create new bucket
Select region (origin bucket)
Enable versioning though!
Create that bucket
Now create a new bucket
Select new Region (replication bucket)
Enable versioning

Now that we have 2 buckets we can set up CRR
Add your files etc...


On the origin bucket select management
Create replciation rule
Name
Enabled
Leave source bucket as it it
Apply all objects
choose a bucket for (destination)
Enter IAM Roles (create new role)
Save
Now select "yes replicate existing objects" for batch operations, however we chose NO

You can enable "Delete marker replication"
for you can delete from one bucket to both

